In any case, to those bitchin' about the spelling changes, they do have an effect on gameplay, and probably should be in the patch message, just not where they are now.  Would've been much better to place them at the end where the UI file changes were made so only people really interested in them had to read down that far.  The point is they have an effect on gameplay, if someone's going strictly off a quest writeup listing on a message board or website, these changes are gonna be important to be aware of.  Listing them makes more sense if you work in CS and can see the thousands of calls from newbie monks demanding to know why their faction quest hotkeys no longer work.  <br>
